  • Method Details

    • getMappedDomainNameForIP

      protected String getMappedDomainNameForIP(String ip)
      IP to domain name mapping support. This matches the given IP string against a user-set list of mappings. This enables applications which do not properly support the SOCKS5 DOMAINNAME feature to be used with I2P.
      Parameters:
      ip - The IP address to check.
      Returns:
      The domain name if a mapping is found, or null otherwise.
      Since:
      0.9.5
